    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The vehicle features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally rigid with no subframe issues. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the double-VANOS system and valvetrain operate at peak performance. While the aesthetics show minor road use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and technical integrity, making it an ideal candidate for the purist driver.",
